    n=10, α=(1, 10, 0, 0, 0)

  n=3: α=(1,3,3) → K₃ has I=7, not 21. Need i₂=3=C(3,2): complement is empty,
       G=K₃. But I(K₃,2)=7≠21. IMPOSSIBLE for this seq.
